{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent"},"abstract":[{"text":"These ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tokens"}]},{"text":" are defined for components and refer to semantic tokens or raw tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"They can be seen as a kind of bridge between components and in the end primitive values of the design kit.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudstokenscomponent"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"externalID":"OUDSTokensComponent","title":"Tokens for components","roleHeading":"Library","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"ic_design_token_figma_component.png"}],"role":"collection","modules":[{"name":"Tokens for components"}],"symbolKind":"module"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":null,"code":["🧬 Core version: 1.9.0"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Thus if a component need to change for example its "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"background color"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", and if a "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component token"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" is used for it, then only the value of this "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"token"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" should be changed without any modification on the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" definition."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" use "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component tokens","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" exposed through the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"theme","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to token providers to get their style values."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Components tokens are defined and gathered inside ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift protocol"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" so as to be exposed then through implementation of ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" thanks to dedicated tokens providers.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because we choose to split responsabilities and objects into their own modules, we faced troubles to make possible for children themes or providers to override properties declared in ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"protocols","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" and defined in ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"extensions","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"That is the reason why tokens are exposed as ","type":"text"},{"code":"@objc open","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to be available and overridable anywhere.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Example with "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Declare some component tokens for buttons with properties they must apply","public protocol ButtonComponentTokens {","    var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { get }","    var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { get }","    var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { get }","}","","\/\/ There is an existing provider for such tokens","open class OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider { }","","\/\/ Define the components tokens exposed through the theme thanks to provider","extension OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","    \/\/ Raw tokens can be used","","    @objc open var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._600 }","    ","    \/\/ And also semantic tokens","","    @objc open var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthThicker }","    @objc open var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.radiusMedium }","    @objc open var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","    @objc open var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSpacious }","}","","\/\/ This provider is then exposed through OUDSTheme as an AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"]},{"anchor":"How-to-use-component-tokens","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"How to use component tokens"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"In fact, the component tokens are declared and gathered in ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift protocol"}]},{"text":" so as to force any theme to implement them, and also to allow any theme to expose such properties whathever the implementation of the theme is, across providers.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}]},{"text":" have for values ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"raw tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"semantic tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":", and in the end for values primitive types, and all these tokens are declared with "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"type aliases"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" refering all together, you can handle a "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"component token","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" directly in your view because the final value will be used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Thus, get the theme and call the needed property with some helpers."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct SomeView: View {","","    @Environment(\\.theme) private var theme \/\/ Supposed you used in your root view the `OUDSThemeableView` to register the theme","    @Environment(\\.colorScheme) private var colorScheme","","    var body: some View {","        Button {","            \/\/ Some action","        } label: {","            Text(\"Some label\")","                .cornerRadius(theme.button.buttonBorderRadius)","        }","        .padding(.leading, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronStart)","        .padding(.trailing, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd)","        .background(theme.button.colorBgStrongEnabledMono)","        .overlay(","            RoundedRectangle(cornerRadius: theme.button.buttonBorderRadius)","                .stroke(Color.blue, lineWidth: theme.button.buttonBorderWidthDefault)","        )","    }","\/*","    - The theme provides border semantic tokens \"buttonBorderRadius\" and \"buttonBorderWidthDefault\"","    - The theme provides a color semantic token \"colorBgStrongEnabledMono\"","    - The theme provides spaces semantic token \"spacePaddingInlineChevronStart\" and \"spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd\"","*\/","}","","\/\/ Do not forget in your app to use the `OUDSThemeableView` for your theme, e.g. `OrangeTheme`","@main","struct DesignToolbox: App {","","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","                ...","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The components tokens are wrapped in tokens provider acessible through the themes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"rows":[[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components tokens provider"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Target component"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For badges like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSBadge","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"button","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For buttons like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bulletList"}],"type":"paragraph"}],[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"For list of elements with bullets","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"checkbox"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For checkboxes like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckbox"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"text":" and their indeterminate variants","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For chips like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSSuggestionChip","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSFilterChip","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"controlItem"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Shared and sued for switch, checkbox and radio items layouts","type":"text"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"divider"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For dividers like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSHorizontalDivider"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSVerticalDivider"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"icon"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For components containing icons like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"link","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For links like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSLink"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"pinCodeInput"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"quantityInput","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"radioButton"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For radio components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadio"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSRadioItem"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"selectInput","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"skeleton"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"switch","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For switch components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitch"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitchItem"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tag"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For tag components like "},{"code":"OUDSTag","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"inputTag","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For input tag components like ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSInputTag"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"textArea","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For text area components like "},{"code":"OUDSTextArea","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"textInput"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For text field input components like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTextInput"}]}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"}]}],"topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/BadgeComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/BulletListComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/CheckboxComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ChipComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ControlItemComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/DividerComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ExpandLinkComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/IconComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/LinkComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/PinCodeInputComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/QuantityInputComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/RadioButtonComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SelectInputComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SkeletonComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/SwitchComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/TagComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/InputTagComponentTokens","doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/TextAre